    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in great shape, ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been super dependable for me. It\u2019s been well-maintained and still looks fantastic inside and out\u2014perfect for someone who wants quality without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
