      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six, featuring a 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been serviced to maintain optimal variable valve timing. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded poly-bushings, and the braking system features refreshed rotors for consistent thermal management. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is mechanically dialed for spirited performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Engine runs smoothly. Interior is well-maintained. All maintenance records available. Minor exterior wear only.",
