    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a fantastic, reliable ride for me and it\u2019s still in really wonderful shape! It runs like a charm and has been super well-maintained, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. It's clean, dependable, and honestly just a joy to drive. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to give me a shout if you have any questions at all!",
