    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and traditional rear-drive dynamics. To address platform-specific requirements, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the cooling system overhauled with an aluminum radiator. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a precise hydraulic steering rack. This is a highly communicative machine that rewards technical drivers with its high-revving ceiling and balanced weight distribution.",
